      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GO FORWARD KENNY (3) jumped from this same draw and was close to the lead throughout before lifting to score (18.27) at this track over 320m in a Grade 5. In form and can measure up again. KOROISAU BANNER (2) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Side Show Bob (18.55) in a Grade 5. Took the lead and boxed on but run over. Expected to be in this for a long way. MISTER ANATOLY (1) stalked the pace then proved too strong in the run home to record his maiden win (18.68) at this track over 320m. Nicely drawn here. Harder here but expected to feature again. STAR PEDRO (4) has ability and must be included among the main hopes.",
